data.actual_result: Clyde would say that you didn't have Discord Nitro and that you would have to upgrade to use emoji.
data.expected_result: Clyde should've said "Sorry, but custom emojis in this channel are disabled."
data.short_description: When you are nitro, and you use custom emoji on a custom-emoji-disabled channel, it says you dont have nitro.
data.steps_to_repro: - Be/Become Nitro - Create/Goto a channel with Custom Emoji disabled - Use a custom emoji - See the message from Clyde.
